on Bishop (Somerset). The placenames derive from Old English <i>rēad</i> ‘red’ + <i>clif</i> ‘cliff, bank, steep slope’ (see also   Rutley  ). A family of the name <i>Radcliffe</i> trace their descent from Sir Nicholas <i>de Radclyffe</i>. He is said to have been a knight who held the major of Radcliffe in Lancashire and served Roger de Poitou, Baron de Marsey in the 11th century."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Radcliffe was born in 1365, in England, United Kingdom. She married Sir Laurence Hamerton. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1365–":"1365–Surnud","1380–1449":"1380–1449","1388–Female":"1388–Surnud","1365–Female":"1365–Surnud","1388":"1388","1365":"1365","1380":"1380","1449":"1449","Swaffham, Norfolk, England":"Swaffham, Norfolk, England","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1365–":"1365–Kuollut","1380–1449":"1380–1449","1388–Female":"1388–Kuollut","1365–Female":"1365–Kuollut","1388":"1388","1365":"1365","1380":"1380","1449":"1449","Swaffham, Norfolk, England":"Swaffham, Norfolk, England","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1365–":"1365–Décédée","1380–1449":"1380–1449","1388–Female":"1388–Décédée","1365–Female":"1365–Décédée","1388":"1388","1365":"1365","1380":"1380","1449":"1449","Swaffham, Norfolk, England":"Swaffham, Norfolk, Angleterre","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Radcliffe est née en 1365, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Sir Laurence Hamerton. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1365–":"1365–Verstorben","1380–1449":"1380–1449","1388–Female":"1388–Verstorben","1365–Female":"1365–Verstorben","1388":"1388","1365":"1365","1380":"1380","1449":"1449","Swaffham, Norfolk, England":"Swaffham, Norfolk, England","England, United Kingdom":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Radcliffe wurde 1365 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hat Sir Laurence Hamerton geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1365–":"1365–Desede","1380–1449